data.text:
My Grandfather, Peter Masterson, pictured outside 19 Newfoundland Street probably pre 1938.

Peter Masterson born 04/10/1890 at 7 Nixon Street, to parents Patrick Masterson and Kate Masterson (nee Costigan).

Peter had two brothers, John and James, and a sister Mary who died at 4 months old in 1889.

Peter Married Honora O'Callaghan at St Laurence O'Toole Church on 19/07/1916.

Peter and Honora (known as Nora), had 6 children, all born a 4 Williams Place, Patrick Joseph (b1917), Peter Edward (b1919), Kathleen Gertrude (b1922), Roseanna Mary (b1925), Michael Joseph (b1927) and my father James Jospeh (b1930).

Peter died 07/12/1953 at 13 Drumcliffe Drive, Cabra West.
